his supporters the way his just tells me that he frankly doesn’t give a damn about the safety of Americans,” Rep. Norma Torres (D-Calif.) said.  “Dangerous, obscene, racist, disgusting, quite frankly un-American,” Rep. Barbara Lee (D-Calif.) said of the comments.  <i>Andrew Desiderio and Burgess Everett contributed to this report. </i>    Article originally published on POLITICO Magazine 
